body.name: WAVLINK AX1800 WiFi 6 Wireless Outdoor Repeater, Long Range Outdoor WiFi with Dual Band PoE IP67 Waterproof,Supports Mesh Extender/AP/Repeater for Farm,Courtyard,RV,Campsite
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Monday, February 19. Order within 13 hrs 17 mins
features: 【Enjoy True WiFi 6 Speed】The next generation of WiFi, complies with IEEE 802.11 ac/a/b/g/n standards.Supports dual-band maximum speed up to 5GHz 1201Mbps and 2.4GHz 574Mbps, avoiding wireless interference & congestion and offering lightning-fast Internet speed. you can enjoy HD videos, smooth gaming, etc. even outdoors.

【Multiple Modes, Flexible Use】You can install it anywhere you want,Place as you like,Equipped with IP67 waterproof enclosure, 15kV ESD protection and 6kV lightning protection, it can work normally in rain/snow/wind/thunder and other bad weather. Supports Mesh, AP, Router, Repeater, AP+Repeater and other modes to meet your different needs and apply to more outdoor use scenarios.

【Seamless WiFi Roaming】The 4x8dBi Fiberglass tube high-gain antennasomnidirectional antennas and two built-in high-power amplifiers provide extreme WiFi coverage and penetration,greatly expanding the WiFi coverage, and eliminating every network dead zone.design for more strong penetration & longer range coverage, ideal for providing Wi-Fi service in big area such as Home,Camping,Factory, Community, Street.

【Optional PoE Power Supply】Supports 802.3AF/AT active PoE and passive PoE, transferring data and charging the product with a single Ethernet cable, so you can install the product outdoors where power outlet is not available,Give you more choice of installation locations. Note: The PoE converter is not waterproof. Please use CAT5E or above cable and the length should not exceed 100m/328ft.

【About After Sales&Note】Please feel free to contact us in the buyer communication if you have any question, We will provide solutions within 8 h,12-month worry free warranty(extra 6 months for registered members) and life-long technical support.Note: If you need to use special characters, please search for 573HX1 in Firmware on the Wavlink website to upgrade the latest firmware.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Unit arrived on time, set up took about an hour, the physical set up was simple, the connection process wasn't as easy. Had to reset once, when you first log on it won't let you change modes until you reset passwords then refresh, then was difficult to log back in and navigate app. Took a little bit to figure out, but got it on the second try. So far I have good reception, haven't checked all areas yet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wow, full coverage over the entire back property
reviews.reviewText: I finally had time to get this Wavlink AX1800 WiFi 6 Outdoor Repeater setup. Holy cow! What a difference it makes. The thing is huge so it shouldn't be too surprising. The instructions were easy to follow, but if you have ever set something like this up before, it's very similar. Once I got the cable ran and the repeater mounter, setup went pretty quick. After getting everything setup, I took a stroll around the property and I am getting a very strong signal all the way at the edges of the property where I was getting nothing before. Very happy with this repeater!
